  <uuid rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">77687b5eac514cdd8d4cf1c</uuid>
  <does rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean">true</does>
  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Social Network Posting Tools and Share Features You can access various social network posting and sharing tools through our Services that are operated by third parties including a share button that allows you to post links to content and features that you believe will be of interest to others on your social network pages When you visit a page that includes one of these sharing tools the third-party company that operates the tool may be collecting information about your browser device and online activity through its own tracking technologies and subject to its own separate privacy policy which may differ from ours</evidence>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

